hopobject.body: We'd like to offer you the job focus factor reviews consumer reports Amid the fights, tears and drunken rants on this season's 'Jersey Shore,' the one thing that seems to stand out the most is J-Woww's ever-changing face. Following the fourth season premiere of the hit MTV reality show, a number of viewers were shocked by the buxom brunette's dramatic weight loss and gaunt face. With her plumper lips and tighter skin being the subject of speculation in recent weeks, J-Woww has finally broken her silence to reveal a rather surprising claim: She hasn't had any additional plastic surgery. 'If I got work done, I would be open to talking about it,' she tells In Touch.'[But] I didn't.'
